                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus/><div style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;">Fol. 2r:&#160;Ownership note (incomplete).</span></div><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">Fol. 2r:</span></span><span unicode="" style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 10pt;"> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4936;&#4961; &#4632;&#4941;&#4725;&#4628;&#4961; &#4645;&#4651;&#4845;&#4961; &#4773;&#4756;&#4961; &#4676;&#4661;&#4961; &#4739;&#4845;</span></span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 10pt;"> </span><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#8230;</span></span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>Incomplete note written in pen, stating that the book belongs to qes (priest)... [illegible].</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus/><p><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">Fol. 2r: Transaction note.</span></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">Fol.2r: </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4776;&#4768;&#4726;&#4961; &#4768;&#4661;&#4872;&#4854;&#4637;&#4961; &#4931;&#4821;&#4849;&#4961; &#4840;&#4632;&#4941;&#4724;&#4628;&#4961;</span></span><span style="line-height: 115%;">[sic]</span><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4645;&#4651;&#4845;&#4961; &#4980;&#4709;&#4653;&#4961; &#4720;&#4672;&#4709;&#4840;&#4961; &#4768;&#4622;&#4613;&#4961; &#4773;&#4756;&#4961; &#4676;&#4661;&#4961; &#4739;&#4845;&#4616;&#4961; &#4872;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961; &#4635;&#4653;&#4843;&#4637;</span></span></span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note is written in pencil. It states that priest (qes) Ḫaylä Gebrä Maryam has received 30 Bǝrr from ʾAsgädom Ṣaʿǝdu for the Ms.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus/><div style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;">Fol. 4r: Donation note.</span></div><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;">Fol. 4r: [l.n.] </span><span style="font-size: large;">&#4768;&#4637;&#4720; &#4637;&#4613; &#4845;&#4613;&#4961; &#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4941;&#4961; &#4632;&#4941;&#4725;&#4628;&#4840;&#4661;&#4961;</span><span style="font-size: small;">[sic]</span> <span style="font-size: large;">&#4824;&#4720;&#4643;&#4840;&#4896;&#4961; &#4704;&#4757;&#4811;&#4840;&#4961; &#4768;&#4726; &#4768;&#4661;&#4872;&#4854;&#4637;&#4961; &#4923;&#4773;&#4849;&#4961; &#4808;&#4808;&#4624;&#4710;&#4961; &#4776;&#4710;<span style="font-size: small;">{</span>&#4723;<span style="font-size: small;">}</span>&#4961; &#4768;&#4705;&#4752;&#4961; &#4720;&#4781;&#4616;&#4961; &#4611;&#4635;&#4758;&#4725;</span>[sic]</p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note is written in pencil, it states that Asgädom Ṣaʾǝdu donated the book to the church of Abunä Täklä Haymanot (ʾAraʿro Täklä Haymanot).</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- King Ḫaylä Śǝllase and Metropolitan Basǝlyos are mentioned in the supplication formula on fol. 52vb.&#xD;
- Spaces for rubricated names were left unfilled throughout the Ms.&#xD;
- Illegible notes written in pen and pencil: fol. 3r.&#xD;
- Scribbles in the margin: fols. 27r, 59r.&#xD;
- Lacunas: fols. 37vb, 38vb, 41rb, 42rb, 43rab, 43rab, 44ra.&#xD;
- Single Ethiopic letters or numerals are written in the upper margin: fols. 9r, 11r, 15r, 21r, 22v, 23v, 26v, 34v, 42r, 47v.</item>
                     </list>
